snippet.title: Super Mombo Quest | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mombo Quest is available now for PC, mobile and consoles! Get ready to make some combos 👅

Super Mombo Quest is an action-packed precision platformer! 👾💥💨 A metroidvania with classic arcade mechanics, featuring some crazy combat, challenging combos and plenty of collectibles - all in a huge interconnected world!

___________________________
Play now!

✔️Steam https://bit.ly/SMQSteam
✔️Play Store https://bit.ly/PlayStoreSMQ
✔️App Store https://bit.ly/SMQAppStore
✔️Nintendo Switch https://bit.ly/SMQSwitch
✔️Xbox (soon)
✔️PlayStation (soon)
